name: Gnikool Ssalg
description:
You are given a string. Reverse its characters. Input The only line of input
contains a string between 1 and 100 characters long. Each character of the
string has ASCII-code between 33 (exclamation mark) and 126 (tilde),
inclusive. Output Output the characters of this string in reverse order.
Examples Input secrofedoc Output codeforces Input !ssalg-gnikool5 Output
5looking-glass!
